2:[["$","$L7",null,{"headerBgImage":"/images/articles/news-ai-robot.jpg"}],["$","article",null,{"className":"article-page news-article-page","style":{"padding":0},"children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrapper","style":{"padding":"0 24px"},"children":["$","span",null,{"className":"blog-entry-category","children":"19 March 2026"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"article-wrapper","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"article-content","children":[["$","h1",null,{"children":"OpenClaw 3.0 发布：AI 助手新纪元"}],["$","div",null,{"dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"<p>OpenClaw 3.0 正式发布了！这一版本带来了众多令人兴奋的新功能和改进，标志着 AI 助手开发进入了一个新的里程碑。</p>\n    \n    <h3>主要更新亮点</h3>\n    <ul>\n    <li><strong>更智能的任务自动化</strong> - 全新的任务调度系统，能够更智能地处理复杂的工作流程</li>\n    <li><strong>增强的插件生态系统</strong> - 支持更多第三方插件，集成能力大幅提升</li>\n    <li><strong>改进的协作能力</strong> - 支持多 Agent 协同工作，更好地处理复杂任务</li>\n    <li><strong>性能优化</strong> - 响应速度提升 40%，内存占用降低 25%</li>\n    <li><strong>全新 UI 设计</strong> - 更现代化的界面，更好的用户体验</li>\n    </ul>\n    \n    <h3>开发者体验提升</h3>\n    <p>对于开发者来说，3.0 版本提供了更完善的 SDK 和 API 文档，让集成变得更加简单。新增的调试工具和实时监控功能，大大提升了开发效率。</p>\n    \n    <h3>安全性增强</h3>\n    <p>安全性一直是 OpenClaw 的核心关注点。3.0 版本引入了更严格的权限控制和数据加密机制，确保用户数据的安全。</p>\n    \n    <p>如果你想了解更多关于 OpenClaw 3.0 的详细信息，可以访问官方网站或关注官方社区。</p>"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"share-links","children":[["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"Twitter","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-twitter"}]}],["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"LinkedIn","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-linkedin-in"}]}],["$","a",null,{"href":"#","title":"Facebook","children":["$","i",null,{"className":"fab fa-facebook-f"}]}]]}]]}]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-light pt-4 pb-4","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container","children":[["$","h3",null,{"style":{"marginBottom":"24px","fontSize":"18px","fontWeight":700},"children":"其他新闻"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"posts-grid","children":[["$","div","astral-join-openai",{"className":"col-12 col-md